WEBVTT

01:40.440 --> 01:45.950
[Speed and Love]

01:46.270 --> 01:48.700
[Episode 3]

02:36.530 --> 02:38.530
Do you remember what a navigator is?

02:40.340 --> 02:41.810
As a racer,

02:41.860 --> 02:44.440
you need to be aware of
your car's condition and road conditions

02:44.440 --> 02:45.370
at all times.

02:46.390 --> 02:47.590
This is the radiator.

02:47.910 --> 02:49.910
This is the oil dipstick.

02:54.780 --> 02:55.710
What do you hear?

02:56.090 --> 02:57.090
Bubbling sounds.

02:57.130 --> 02:58.060
Bubbles?

02:58.680 --> 02:59.350
Mu,

02:59.560 --> 03:01.020
sit in the passenger seat.

03:02.910 --> 03:04.590
Be my navigator.

03:11.160 --> 03:11.880
Left!

03:13.960 --> 03:15.630
Forward! Go!

03:17.190 --> 03:17.880
I remember.

03:18.280 --> 03:19.470
I need your help now.

03:20.590 --> 03:21.790
The password is 1120.

03:22.160 --> 03:23.440
Open the digital app.

03:25.400 --> 03:27.030
Find the pinned
group location information.

03:27.030 --> 03:28.290
Tell me the direction.

03:41.560 --> 03:42.890
They crashed behind us.

03:43.070 --> 03:44.070
What should we do?

03:44.280 --> 03:44.880
Which way?

03:45.120 --> 03:46.560
They crashed behind us!

03:46.790 --> 03:47.840
Tell me the route.

03:53.470 --> 03:55.160
Be careful.
About 800 meters ahead there's...

03:55.160 --> 03:56.560
I don't know what that is.

03:56.630 --> 03:58.190
There are three possible roads nearby.

03:58.190 --> 04:00.560
The distances are similar.
The road conditions...

04:00.560 --> 04:02.360
I can't see the road conditions.

04:04.160 --> 04:05.030
Choose one.

04:05.750 --> 04:06.750
When we reach the east side,

04:06.750 --> 04:09.150
make a sharp 90-degree turn
into the second curve.

04:09.150 --> 04:10.410
I'll follow your lead.

04:18.070 --> 04:19.930
There's a fork ahead. Turn right.

04:58.030 --> 04:59.110
Brandy?

04:59.560 --> 05:01.620
Didn't he say he wasn't coming today?

05:57.240 --> 05:58.170
Listen to me now.

05:58.310 --> 05:59.440
After this curve,

05:59.750 --> 06:01.070
I'll count down from five.

06:01.070 --> 06:02.440
Then you grab the steering wheel.

06:02.440 --> 06:03.190
How?

06:03.390 --> 06:04.320
With your hands.

06:12.710 --> 06:13.480
Five.

06:17.510 --> 06:18.270
Four.

06:24.230 --> 06:25.160
Jin Zhao, look!

06:26.120 --> 06:26.880
Three.

06:32.190 --> 06:32.950
Two.

06:36.440 --> 06:37.000
One.

06:37.050 --> 06:37.730
Grab it!

06:51.470 --> 06:53.700
♪ Make it fast, never slow down ♪

06:53.720 --> 06:56.200
♪ Show off my extraordinary form ♪

06:56.220 --> 06:57.340
♪ Speeding love ♪

06:57.360 --> 06:58.760
♪ Whether I succeed or fail ♪

06:58.790 --> 07:00.930
♪ I just want to be free ♪

07:00.960 --> 07:03.520
♪ Shining star, heart on fire ♪

07:03.540 --> 07:05.790
♪ The odds of winning are 100% ♪

07:05.820 --> 07:08.640
♪ Make my name be known
throughout the world ♪

07:08.660 --> 07:10.740
♪ You just wait and see ♪

07:10.760 --> 07:13.140
♪ Make it fast, never slow down ♪

07:13.170 --> 07:15.220
♪ Show off my extraordinary form ♪

07:15.240 --> 07:16.640
♪ Speeding love ♪

07:16.660 --> 07:17.890
♪ Whether I succeed or fail ♪

07:17.910 --> 07:20.090
♪ I just want to be free ♪

07:20.110 --> 07:22.680
♪ Shining star, heart on fire ♪

07:22.700 --> 07:25.010
♪ The odds of winning are 100% ♪

07:25.030 --> 07:27.500
♪ Make my name be known
throughout the world ♪

07:27.530 --> 07:29.860
♪ You just wait and see ♪

07:37.070 --> 07:38.800
Stay by my side and don't speak.

07:39.750 --> 07:40.600
Let's go.

07:48.140 --> 07:49.780
Brandy!

07:50.630 --> 07:52.570
Didn't you say you weren't coming today?

07:52.570 --> 07:53.770
I didn't plan to come,

07:54.430 --> 07:56.190
but Wan Shengbang's little minions

07:56.190 --> 07:57.680
came at me like rabid dogs

07:58.100 --> 07:59.610
and forced me onto the track.

07:59.610 --> 08:02.410
Don't bring your personal issues
to the alliance.

08:02.710 --> 08:03.840
Then go talk to them.

08:04.600 --> 08:06.000
I just want to make money.

08:19.190 --> 08:20.480
Brandy!

08:20.840 --> 08:22.590
I've told you

08:22.840 --> 08:24.910
that we don't allow outsiders here.

08:34.409 --> 08:35.669
She's not an outsider.

08:36.880 --> 08:38.080
She's my girlfriend.

08:39.480 --> 08:40.320
Girlfriend?

08:43.960 --> 08:44.720
Yes.

08:46.410 --> 08:49.070
She recently suspected
I'm seeing someone else

08:50.100 --> 08:52.030
because I disappear every night.

08:52.790 --> 08:54.200
If I didn't bring her along,

08:54.200 --> 08:56.400
she would've broken up with me tonight.

09:02.780 --> 09:04.140
Are you still mad at me?

09:06.720 --> 09:07.910
I can't believe it.

09:08.720 --> 09:11.120
Brandy, you're completely wrapped around

09:11.360 --> 09:12.200
this little girl's finger.

09:12.200 --> 09:14.660
One mention of breaking up
and you've caved.

09:19.030 --> 09:20.490
I can't dote on her enough.

09:21.390 --> 09:22.850
How can I break up with her?

09:34.030 --> 09:35.560
Go back and sweet-talk her.

09:40.130 --> 09:40.840
Take this.

09:43.150 --> 09:44.210
Come here, Brandy.

09:46.660 --> 09:47.610
Wait for me here.

09:52.670 --> 09:53.430
What is it?

09:53.880 --> 09:54.600
Girl,

09:55.000 --> 09:55.750
come here!

09:57.360 --> 09:58.750
So beautiful, girl!

10:24.200 --> 10:25.000
Brandy.

10:28.810 --> 10:31.250
What's the price for your navigator?

10:38.200 --> 10:39.080
Sorry,

10:40.110 --> 10:41.110
she's priceless.

10:54.270 --> 10:55.180
I'm cold.

11:18.850 --> 11:21.960
♪ I leave after your curtain call ♪

11:24.660 --> 11:27.860
♪ I ask the tired bird ♪

11:28.650 --> 11:31.710
♪ About your news ♪

11:33.970 --> 11:37.620
♪ You're too serious in
both your passion and silence ♪

11:39.940 --> 11:45.120
♪ That's why you're always
covered in scars ♪

11:46.630 --> 11:50.230
♪ If darkness can stop the pain ♪

11:50.500 --> 11:55.690
♪ I'll let you sleep a bit longer ♪

11:57.250 --> 12:01.260
♪ I'll stay by your side tonight ♪

12:04.110 --> 12:09.230
♪ I want to meet the dusk with you ♪

12:09.570 --> 12:13.450
♪ Then stay with me until dawn ♪

12:14.220 --> 12:20.260
♪ Our moment together
feels like a lifetime ♪

12:21.010 --> 12:24.660
♪ Your remaining warmth before dawn ♪

12:24.830 --> 12:28.940
♪ Is enough for me to sink in soberly ♪

12:29.410 --> 12:33.200
♪ But I'm still waiting
for every dawn and dusk ♪

12:33.230 --> 12:37.160
♪ To run towards you again ♪

12:38.190 --> 12:42.020
Even if I have only you in my arms

12:39.910 --> 12:41.710
My girlfriend gets cold easily.

12:42.290 --> 12:46.520
♪ I want to meet the dusk with you ♪

12:42.800 --> 12:44.260
I need to take her home now.

12:44.880 --> 12:45.960
Sure.

12:46.570 --> 12:50.330
♪ Then stay with me until dawn ♪

12:50.980 --> 12:56.770
♪ Our moment together
feels like a lifetime ♪

12:57.690 --> 13:01.330
♪ Your remaining warmth before dawn ♪

13:01.440 --> 13:05.830
♪ Is enough for me to sink in soberly ♪

13:06.190 --> 13:08.190
♪ But I'm still waiting ♪

13:07.600 --> 13:08.770
Take care, bro!

13:08.470 --> 13:10.120
♪ For every dawn and dusk ♪

13:10.140 --> 13:14.070
♪ To run towards you again ♪

13:14.210 --> 13:17.870
♪ Until I can embrace you ♪

13:18.580 --> 13:20.580
♪ Can you hear me ♪

13:20.600 --> 13:22.420
♪ Your heart also aches, right ♪

13:22.440 --> 13:26.160
♪ Those days and nights were not a waste ♪

13:26.180 --> 13:32.100
♪ How long will it take to answer ♪

13:35.140 --> 13:39.690
♪ Meet the dusk with you ♪

13:39.580 --> 13:40.550
[Fast horse The group leader has disbanded]

13:39.900 --> 13:43.800
♪ Then stay with me until dawn ♪

13:41.680 --> 13:42.220
[The group has been deleted by the admin]
[The group is muted]

13:44.270 --> 13:49.670
♪ Our moment together
feels like a lifetime ♪

13:51.160 --> 13:54.840
♪ Your remaining warmth before dawn ♪

13:54.860 --> 13:59.260
♪ Is enough for me to sink in soberly ♪

13:59.430 --> 14:01.430
♪ But I'm still waiting ♪

14:01.610 --> 14:03.320
♪ For every dawn and dusk ♪

14:03.340 --> 14:06.780
♪ To run towards you again ♪

14:07.690 --> 14:11.790
♪ Until I can embrace you ♪

14:13.550 --> 14:17.190
♪ For a lifetime ♪

14:26.030 --> 14:27.120
Open the envelope.

14:36.480 --> 14:38.210
This is what you wanted to know.

14:38.420 --> 14:39.420
For money?

14:42.630 --> 14:43.430
What else?

14:44.170 --> 14:45.570
What else could it be for?

14:49.960 --> 14:51.690
That guy from earlier crashed.

14:53.200 --> 14:54.150
He won't die.

14:55.790 --> 14:57.120
What do you mean by that?

14:57.840 --> 14:58.960
What if something serious happened

14:58.960 --> 15:00.490
and they trace it back to us?

15:01.270 --> 15:02.840
There are so many accidents
across the country.

15:02.840 --> 15:04.960
They always blame nearby vehicles
when something happens.

15:04.960 --> 15:06.350
What if someone called the police?

15:06.350 --> 15:07.950
Who could trace it back to us?

15:08.330 --> 15:09.930
Isn't there that group chat?

15:12.200 --> 15:12.840
No, wait.

15:13.390 --> 15:14.840
The group was just deleted.

15:14.840 --> 15:15.840
It was read-only.

15:16.000 --> 15:17.800
No chat history was left behind.

15:18.070 --> 15:19.030
The transaction was done in cash,

15:19.030 --> 15:20.230
so it can't be traced.

15:20.790 --> 15:21.910
The roads in the area

15:21.910 --> 15:24.640
probably don't even have
surveillance cameras.

15:37.270 --> 15:39.000
Even if it's all well-hidden, so what?

15:39.000 --> 15:40.880
What if something really happens?

15:40.880 --> 15:41.720
For money,

15:42.150 --> 15:43.720
are you willing to risk your life?

15:43.720 --> 15:44.670
Today, it was him.

15:44.670 --> 15:46.130
What if it's you tomorrow?

15:49.030 --> 15:50.360
Do you really have to

15:51.840 --> 15:53.480
live on the edge like this?

16:01.270 --> 16:03.150
Live on the edge?

16:06.550 --> 16:08.550
Then how do you think I should live?

16:10.600 --> 16:11.390
I don't know.

16:12.600 --> 16:13.960
But not like this.

16:14.840 --> 16:15.970
At the very least...

16:17.320 --> 16:20.050
At the very least,
it should be stable and secure.

16:27.550 --> 16:28.750
Since you don't know,

16:28.880 --> 16:29.790
let me tell you.

16:31.720 --> 16:33.030
When Jin Qiang and I first came here,

16:33.030 --> 16:34.150
we had nowhere to live.

16:34.150 --> 16:35.350
We rented a basement.

16:35.510 --> 16:36.990
No windows, no light.

16:37.390 --> 16:38.720
Day was just like night.

16:39.430 --> 16:40.880
Every time it rained,

16:40.990 --> 16:42.630
it would flood up to our legs.

16:43.150 --> 16:44.790
Homework, backpacks, mattresses...

16:44.790 --> 16:45.670
They'd all be submerged.

16:45.670 --> 16:48.070
Even the dead rats
would float in the water!

16:49.910 --> 16:52.170
We had to put tables together to sleep on.

16:52.390 --> 16:53.150
Then the next day,

16:53.150 --> 16:55.480
we'd scoop the water out bucket by bucket.

16:55.960 --> 16:57.240
Later, someone referred Jin Qiang

16:57.240 --> 16:58.640
to do some earthwork job.

16:58.840 --> 17:00.320
It required a referral fee.

17:00.320 --> 17:02.050
Jin Qiang gave all his money
to that person.

17:02.050 --> 17:04.790
That person's phone number
immediately became disconnected.

17:04.790 --> 17:07.390
We couldn't even afford
the basement anymore.

17:08.560 --> 17:10.160
I had to sleep on the streets,

17:10.280 --> 17:11.880
on pedestrian bridges,
in underground passages,

17:11.880 --> 17:14.010
and you tell me money isn't important?

17:31.520 --> 17:32.280
Later...

17:35.120 --> 17:36.920
He finally found a reliable job.

17:37.710 --> 17:39.640
He worked as a chef in a restaurant.

17:40.230 --> 17:42.090
That's where he met Zhao Meijuan.

17:42.720 --> 17:44.780
It was Zhao Meijuan's first marriage

17:46.150 --> 17:47.480
and Jin Qiang's second.

17:48.150 --> 17:49.280
He had no money

17:49.600 --> 17:50.660
and was raising me.

17:50.880 --> 17:52.280
The two of them scraped together
enough money

17:52.280 --> 17:53.480
to open a restaurant.

17:55.400 --> 17:57.200
They worked from dawn till dusk,

17:59.240 --> 18:01.700
but their earnings
barely covered the rent.

18:04.390 --> 18:06.650
Whenever school asked for tuition fees,

18:07.600 --> 18:09.330
I could only stand at their door

18:10.990 --> 18:12.790
with the payment slip in my hand.

18:14.230 --> 18:16.360
It was just two or three hundred bucks,

18:17.050 --> 18:18.980
but I couldn't bring myself to ask.

18:26.050 --> 18:28.050
Do you think money isn't important?

18:37.380 --> 18:38.950
Jin Xin needs surgery.

18:41.900 --> 18:43.700
It's congenital heart disease.

18:44.800 --> 18:46.470
Besides the surgery costs,

18:46.840 --> 18:48.990
there are also expensive treatment fees.

18:48.990 --> 18:50.520
Jin Qiang is already broke.

18:50.880 --> 18:53.150
This is just
adding insult to the injury for him.

18:53.150 --> 18:54.430
For money, he even...

19:04.680 --> 19:06.280
What do you think I should do?

19:09.820 --> 19:11.750
Stand by and watch him suffer?

19:16.230 --> 19:17.390
Jin Qiang never gave up on me,

19:17.390 --> 19:19.250
even in the most difficult times.

19:22.400 --> 19:23.770
Should I turn my back

19:25.880 --> 19:27.490
on your dad?

19:34.230 --> 19:35.190
Does Mom...

19:37.230 --> 19:38.520
know about all this?

19:39.520 --> 19:41.850
What difference does it make if she knows?

19:42.880 --> 19:45.340
What difference does it make
if she doesn't?

19:48.160 --> 19:49.220
They're divorced.

19:55.560 --> 19:56.600
Even so,

19:58.040 --> 19:58.970
you shouldn't be

19:59.470 --> 20:01.630
doing such dangerous things.

20:01.910 --> 20:03.910
If it makes money, it's worth doing.

20:04.040 --> 20:06.100
What's wrong with living on the edge?

20:06.150 --> 20:07.190
If I'm dead,

20:07.720 --> 20:09.440
why does it matter if I'm on the edge?

20:09.440 --> 20:10.240
Jin Zhao,

20:10.730 --> 20:12.590
why won't you take the right path,

20:12.880 --> 20:15.210
instead of going down this dark alleyway?

20:26.370 --> 20:27.090
Let go.

20:27.390 --> 20:28.150
No.

20:28.300 --> 20:29.280
Do you think

20:29.280 --> 20:31.540
no one in this world
can keep you in check?

20:41.190 --> 20:42.720
You want to keep me in check?

20:42.800 --> 20:43.950
By what right?

20:45.080 --> 20:46.140
Are you still a Jin?

20:46.950 --> 20:48.880
You've even changed your surname.

20:49.530 --> 20:51.360
If you've forgotten your surname,

20:51.360 --> 20:52.620
then let me remind you.

20:54.080 --> 20:54.880
Jiang...

20:57.200 --> 20:58.000
Mu.

21:14.080 --> 21:14.910
So...

21:18.990 --> 21:20.040
This is why you won't come back

21:20.040 --> 21:21.760
to see us, right?

21:28.430 --> 21:29.430
You blame Mom.

21:32.690 --> 21:35.090
You blame her
for leaving Dad with nothing.

21:38.470 --> 21:39.470
You hate her,

21:41.430 --> 21:42.360
don't you?

22:27.710 --> 22:28.430
Okay.

22:53.220 --> 22:54.660
Zhao Meijuan called me.

22:56.880 --> 22:57.710
Go back.

22:59.120 --> 22:59.880
I won't.

23:01.150 --> 23:02.350
What will it take for you to go back?

23:02.350 --> 23:03.480
Promise me first.

23:17.470 --> 23:18.470
Promise you what?

23:18.670 --> 23:20.150
Promise me you'll find a real job

23:20.150 --> 23:21.210
and stop this crap.

23:21.520 --> 23:22.180
Otherwise,

23:22.320 --> 23:24.250
neither of us will go back tonight.

23:35.640 --> 23:36.320
You...

23:49.800 --> 23:50.560
Brother.

23:56.060 --> 23:57.370
Let's go home.

23:59.950 --> 24:00.910
What did you say?

24:06.450 --> 24:07.690
I'll take you home.

24:09.880 --> 24:10.910
What home?

24:14.670 --> 24:15.910
I don't have a home.

24:18.630 --> 24:19.430
You do.

24:20.040 --> 24:21.190
The old house in Nanjing

24:21.190 --> 24:22.710
that we used to live in.

24:30.980 --> 24:32.980
You're not going to Canada anymore?

24:35.080 --> 24:35.840
Nope.

24:36.080 --> 24:37.210
I've made up my mind.

24:37.360 --> 24:38.800
I'm going to take you back to China,

24:38.800 --> 24:39.710
to Nanjing.

24:39.840 --> 24:40.970
From now on, we'll live together

24:40.970 --> 24:42.250
in that old house,

24:42.430 --> 24:44.360
never to be separated again, okay?

24:45.840 --> 24:47.080
I can make money.

24:47.600 --> 24:48.470
I'm capable.

24:48.530 --> 24:50.730
I can give you a stable life.

24:52.190 --> 24:53.150
When we go back,

24:53.470 --> 24:54.990
you can continue your studies

24:54.990 --> 24:55.950
and your writing.

24:55.950 --> 24:57.800
I won't let you fight anymore,

24:58.360 --> 24:59.960
and I won't let you be in pain.

25:00.280 --> 25:00.940
From now on,

25:01.120 --> 25:02.320
I'll protect you.

25:09.630 --> 25:10.600
Trust me.

25:12.510 --> 25:14.030
I can definitely do it.

25:18.460 --> 25:19.170
Brother,

25:19.870 --> 25:21.110
let's go back.

25:34.990 --> 25:36.150
I can't go back.

26:07.150 --> 26:08.990
You can't control him.

26:09.560 --> 26:10.320
Yes,

26:11.320 --> 26:13.320
you couldn't beat him in the ring.

26:15.190 --> 26:16.110
I accept that,

26:16.700 --> 26:17.960
and I'll put up with it.

26:18.000 --> 26:20.250
But how can your driving skills
be worse than his too?

26:20.250 --> 26:21.550
There won't be a next time.

26:21.550 --> 26:23.240
There won't be a next time!

26:23.910 --> 26:25.800
There won't be a next time!

26:26.120 --> 26:26.970
Get lost!

27:23.430 --> 27:24.360
Thank you.

27:29.430 --> 27:30.560
Jin Qiang called.

27:31.730 --> 27:33.660
He said your mom arrived in Manshi.

27:37.770 --> 27:38.970
Let me take you there.

27:41.110 --> 27:41.910
Okay.

28:34.190 --> 28:35.150
Do you...

28:36.430 --> 28:37.800
want to say hello?

28:39.910 --> 28:40.560
No.

28:44.950 --> 28:45.670
Go ahead.

28:59.630 --> 29:00.190
Mu,

29:00.470 --> 29:01.670
actually, your Uncle Chris

29:01.670 --> 29:03.040
cares about you very much.

29:03.040 --> 29:05.770
He's already arranged
a school for you in Canada.

29:05.840 --> 29:07.230
You can continue your studies

29:07.230 --> 29:08.600
and further education there.

29:08.600 --> 29:09.600
I won't go.

29:10.230 --> 29:12.290
If not Canada, then where will you go?

29:13.230 --> 29:14.490
I've already decided.

29:14.600 --> 29:16.650
After graduating, I'll stay in China.

29:16.650 --> 29:18.050
I won't go anywhere else.

29:18.190 --> 29:20.230
This time, come back with me.

29:20.560 --> 29:22.160
Put everything aside for now

29:22.280 --> 29:23.890
and pass the IELTS exam, okay?

29:23.890 --> 29:26.300
I won't pass it.
I don't want to go abroad.

29:26.710 --> 29:27.760
I've said that I'll stay

29:27.760 --> 29:28.910
in that old house in Nanjing.

29:28.910 --> 29:30.710
I don't want to go anywhere else.

29:31.430 --> 29:32.760
I'm planning on selling

29:33.230 --> 29:34.430
the house in Nanjing.

29:35.190 --> 29:37.430
Why would you sell a perfectly fine house?

29:37.430 --> 29:39.630
I've already married your Uncle Chris.

29:39.670 --> 29:41.910
He has many properties
and businesses there.

29:41.910 --> 29:44.340
I've decided to settle down with him
in Canada.

29:44.340 --> 29:46.470
That's also where I plan on retiring to.

29:46.470 --> 29:47.710
So, why would I keep

29:47.710 --> 29:48.910
a house in China?

29:49.150 --> 29:50.080
It's useless.

29:50.190 --> 29:51.190
How is it useless?

29:51.310 --> 29:52.440
Why do you trust him so much?

29:52.440 --> 29:53.360
Aren't you afraid that one day he might—

29:53.360 --> 29:53.900
Mu!

30:02.320 --> 30:03.150
Well...

30:03.800 --> 30:05.130
I'll go check on things.

30:16.710 --> 30:17.390
Mom,

30:17.520 --> 30:19.040
how can you sell the house?

30:19.070 --> 30:19.910
Have you thought about

30:19.910 --> 30:21.430
if things don't work out
between you two in the future?

30:21.430 --> 30:23.430
Where will you live when you come back?

30:23.430 --> 30:24.710
Whether I sell the house or not,

30:24.710 --> 30:26.040
I'll never abandon you.

30:26.360 --> 30:27.910
No matter if you settle abroad

30:27.910 --> 30:29.190
or live in China,

30:29.470 --> 30:31.800
I'll set aside
a large sum of money for you.

30:31.860 --> 30:34.230
This isn't something
for you to worry about,

30:34.230 --> 30:34.880
okay?

30:34.990 --> 30:36.290
Do you think I'm worried about money?

30:36.290 --> 30:38.230
I'm worried about you being deceived.

30:38.230 --> 30:38.950
Enough.

30:39.950 --> 30:40.810
I don't want you

30:40.990 --> 30:42.390
to say such things again.

30:44.480 --> 30:45.800
This topic ends here.

30:57.910 --> 30:59.520
Is that Jin Zhao?

31:06.990 --> 31:08.190
Didn't he leave?

31:09.530 --> 31:10.730
Why did he come back?

31:13.710 --> 31:14.760
Could it be...

31:21.870 --> 31:23.280
He wanted to see...

31:24.230 --> 31:25.280
Mom?

31:26.390 --> 31:28.390
How does he know we're staying here?

31:29.470 --> 31:30.670
He drove me here.

31:31.470 --> 31:32.310
What?

31:33.040 --> 31:34.280
He brought you here?

31:35.190 --> 31:36.430
Your father promised me

31:36.430 --> 31:37.430
that when you came this time,

31:37.430 --> 31:38.690
you two wouldn't meet!

31:38.800 --> 31:39.630
Why?

31:39.880 --> 31:41.410
Why can't we see each other?

31:43.430 --> 31:45.190
Mu, you're grown up now.

31:45.490 --> 31:46.560
Shouldn't you keep some distance

31:46.560 --> 31:47.820
from the opposite sex?

31:48.390 --> 31:50.720
You'd better not see each other too often.

31:50.950 --> 31:52.750
Mom, what are you talking about?

31:52.910 --> 31:54.080
He's Jin Zhao.

31:54.360 --> 31:55.390
I've told you repeatedly

31:55.390 --> 31:56.990
about Jin Zhao's situation.

31:57.150 --> 31:58.880
You are not related by blood.

31:59.390 --> 32:00.590
You're not siblings.

32:00.600 --> 32:01.880
He's not your brother.

32:02.040 --> 32:03.430
I've made myself perfectly clear already.

32:03.430 --> 32:04.690
Don't you understand?

32:06.150 --> 32:06.760
Besides,

32:06.880 --> 32:08.610
he's not even a good person now.

32:11.600 --> 32:13.120
You can't talk about him like that.

32:13.120 --> 32:14.320
Even if we're not related by blood,

32:14.320 --> 32:15.580
he's still my brother.

32:16.190 --> 32:18.630
Back then, your father insisted on
bringing him home.

32:18.630 --> 32:19.950
I was against it,

32:20.360 --> 32:21.360
but your father was stubborn

32:21.360 --> 32:22.600
and insisted.

32:22.910 --> 32:23.950
I already said

32:24.230 --> 32:26.040
this child
would be difficult to discipline.

32:26.040 --> 32:27.630
Bold as brass,

32:27.840 --> 32:30.040
he's bound to get into trouble someday.

32:32.710 --> 32:33.310
Back then,

32:33.320 --> 32:35.230
he called our home repeatedly.

32:35.560 --> 32:36.960
I had warned him already.

32:37.670 --> 32:39.600
I didn't want you two associating.

32:43.840 --> 32:45.300
How could you understand?

32:46.840 --> 32:48.320
If you understood,

32:48.710 --> 32:49.710
you wouldn't have stayed away

32:49.710 --> 32:51.970
for so many years without seeing me once.

32:57.320 --> 32:58.320
What did you say?

32:59.230 --> 33:00.360
He'd called me?

33:01.320 --> 33:02.850
What did you warn him about?

33:02.910 --> 33:04.440
What could I warn him about?

33:04.630 --> 33:06.910
I told him to be sensible,
follow the rules,

33:06.910 --> 33:08.240
and stop pestering you.

33:08.390 --> 33:10.470
After you started middle school,
you weren't little anymore.

33:10.470 --> 33:12.230
Shouldn't he keep his distance?

33:12.230 --> 33:13.840
You think it's still like
when you were children,

33:13.840 --> 33:15.770
talking about sibling affection?

33:18.470 --> 33:19.470
So...

33:20.710 --> 33:23.640
This is the real reason
you didn't come back to see us,

33:24.190 --> 33:25.040
right?

33:35.280 --> 33:36.040
Master.

33:43.600 --> 33:46.060
I'm not in the mood
to play with you right now.

33:49.840 --> 33:51.970
We didn't finish our fight yesterday.

33:54.280 --> 33:55.080
I said,

33:56.040 --> 33:58.500
I'm not in the mood
to play with you right now.

34:34.010 --> 34:35.210
I'm the one beaten up.

34:36.110 --> 34:37.170
Why are you crying?

34:39.080 --> 34:40.110
I've told you repeatedly

34:40.110 --> 34:41.710
about Jin Zhao's situation.

34:41.880 --> 34:43.590
You are not related by blood.

34:44.110 --> 34:45.310
You're not siblings.

34:45.320 --> 34:46.639
He's not your brother.

34:55.320 --> 34:57.380
What's wrong with living on the edge?

34:57.430 --> 34:58.360
If I'm dead,

34:59.030 --> 35:01.030
why does it matter if I'm on the edge?

35:02.430 --> 35:03.960
You want to keep me in check?

35:04.910 --> 35:06.110
By what right?

35:06.790 --> 35:08.720
You've even changed your surname.

35:09.180 --> 35:11.080
If you've forgotten your surname,

35:11.080 --> 35:12.080
let me remind you.

35:12.590 --> 35:13.390
Jiang...

35:15.710 --> 35:16.590
Mu.

35:21.090 --> 35:22.720
Our flight is this afternoon.

35:22.720 --> 35:23.980
I hope to see you there.

35:24.760 --> 35:26.420
I hope you'll think it through

35:26.910 --> 35:28.440
and stop being so stubborn.

36:10.840 --> 36:11.430
Brother,

36:11.550 --> 36:13.280
you haven't called for so long.

36:13.840 --> 36:15.800
I don't know how to find you,

36:16.240 --> 36:17.990
so I can only try writing to you.

36:18.760 --> 36:20.510
I hope you receive it.

36:26.090 --> 36:26.690
Brother,

36:27.090 --> 36:28.550
are you in high school now?

36:29.030 --> 36:31.070
I really want to know how you did
on your high school entrance exam.

36:30.520 --> 36:36.920
♪ Perhaps the weather's damp and mild ♪

36:31.470 --> 36:32.730
I'm sure you did great.

36:33.880 --> 36:35.740
Did you get into a key high school?

36:36.030 --> 36:38.170
Is it because you're busy with high school

36:36.940 --> 36:40.770
♪ Perhaps it's about the habit
of bearing ♪

36:38.590 --> 36:40.990
that you don't have time
to call me anymore?

36:41.480 --> 36:44.770
♪ A certain bitter emotion ♪

36:44.790 --> 36:50.860
♪ For you, it's all too easy ♪

36:46.800 --> 36:48.240
Mom and I are moving.

36:48.760 --> 36:49.960
Mom says we don't need

36:50.160 --> 36:51.760
that old telephone anymore.

36:51.810 --> 36:57.520
♪ To be happy or heartbroken,
as transparent as I can be ♪

36:52.910 --> 36:54.320
We might temporarily move

36:54.320 --> 36:55.650
to a newly rented house.

36:56.070 --> 36:57.720
Once I know the address,

36:57.950 --> 36:59.240
I'll write to you again.

36:58.510 --> 37:04.420
♪ Crossing the line for love,
I've walked 1,000 km ♪

36:59.800 --> 37:01.360
Missing you, Mu.

37:05.760 --> 37:11.920
♪ Brave enough to be sure is my instinct ♪

37:12.070 --> 37:13.230
♪ I believe ♪

37:13.250 --> 37:17.420
♪ Maybe it just takes a little resolve ♪

37:17.680 --> 37:20.910
♪ To turn wishes into shooting stars ♪

37:21.280 --> 37:22.110
Zhao,

37:21.490 --> 37:26.520
♪ Mirroring the eyes that gaze at me ♪

37:22.720 --> 37:24.990
this is my last time writing to you,

37:25.880 --> 37:27.950
because you've never written back.

37:28.740 --> 37:30.820
I feel like I'm writing to thin air.

37:32.590 --> 37:34.390
I'm starting middle school now.

37:34.590 --> 37:36.280
I'll have many new classmates

37:37.110 --> 37:39.030
and I'll make more good friends.

37:39.880 --> 37:40.910
So,

37:40.300 --> 37:46.120
♪ The crash of waves comes and goes ♪

37:41.390 --> 37:42.650
let's end things here.

37:43.110 --> 37:45.070
Never missing you again, Mu.

37:47.140 --> 37:50.620
♪ After leaning on you and hesitation ♪

37:50.840 --> 37:54.120
♪ I've never been so steadfast and true ♪

37:54.280 --> 38:00.120
♪ My love needs to stay clear-eyed ♪

38:00.430 --> 38:01.510
It turns out

38:01.170 --> 38:07.120
♪ After the scorching ache,
I still reach for a sincere heart ♪

38:02.360 --> 38:04.160
that he received all the letters

38:04.160 --> 38:05.470
I sent him.

38:07.070 --> 38:08.390
He read them all.

38:08.470 --> 38:14.370
♪ Crossing the line for love,
I've walked 1,000 km ♪

38:10.550 --> 38:12.590
He even drew me

38:13.240 --> 38:15.030
on every letter.

38:15.730 --> 38:21.870
♪ Brave enough to be sure is my instinct ♪

38:19.280 --> 38:20.550
All these years,

38:21.890 --> 38:27.000
♪ I believe
maybe it just takes a little resolve ♪

38:22.030 --> 38:23.690
Jin Zhao has been just like me.

38:24.880 --> 38:26.840
He's been thinking of me too.

38:27.280 --> 38:30.620
♪ To turn wishes into shooting stars ♪

38:31.230 --> 38:35.620
♪ Mirroring the eyes that gaze at me ♪

38:35.640 --> 38:40.730
♪ Fearless as a moth
darting into the fire ♪

38:40.760 --> 38:48.820
♪ I'd rewrite the ending
of missed chances 1,000 times ♪

38:49.910 --> 38:55.460
♪ Crossing the line for love,
I've walked 1,000 km ♪

38:51.550 --> 38:52.320
Brother,

38:52.550 --> 38:54.280
will you always be good to me?

38:57.060 --> 39:02.960
♪ Brave enough to be sure is my instinct ♪

38:57.470 --> 38:58.840
As long as you don't change,

38:58.840 --> 39:00.100
I won't change either.

39:02.970 --> 39:04.180
♪ I believe ♪

39:04.370 --> 39:08.220
♪ Maybe it just takes a little resolve ♪

39:08.240 --> 39:12.160
♪ To turn wishes into shooting stars ♪

39:12.360 --> 39:17.400
♪ Mirroring the eyes that gaze at me ♪

39:23.150 --> 39:29.970
♪ Crossing the orbit,
stepping into your life ♪
